 1995-15301995-09-130,  ,  ,  ND, 
PrecisAmendment to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES (Article 111.051) whereby Armed Forces personnel would be disqualified from serving as jurors in court martial proceedings if they have been convicted of either a military offence or an indictable offence, as is the case in civil proceedings.
